title: Thomas Dybdahl Live In Concert (27.10.2007, Amsterdam, Paradiso
description:
This concert is a simple FLV rip from Fabchannel (http://www.fabchannel.com/thomas_dybdahl_2007_concert). I simply got sick of watching it using the crappy flash player and wanted to enjoy it with the playback functionality if a proper media player. Neither the video or audio have been transcoded so there is no loss in quality. The video and mp3 audio have simply been extracted from the FLV container and mux&#039;ed using VirtualDub.

The MP3 track has been included as a bonus.

Enjoy this excellent 88 minute concert by Thomas Dybdahl and his talented band :)
